high_descs: Turn to the bath tub to your left.
Pick up the rag in front of the drain, in the bath tub.
Turn to your right and go to the first sink on your left.
Place the rag in the sink, turn the water on, clean the rag, turn the water off, and remove the rag from the sink.
Turn to your left and go back to the bath tub across from you.
Place the rag back in the bath tub, far away from the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag in the bath tub.
